{"tid":1696521,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［回帶］中二生厚德商場玩扶手梯 吊上1/F失手墮樓重傷","createTime":"2019-11-06T08:18:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-07T07:32:35.000Z","uid":124690,"like":2,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"1e6490b68536e7873233eb1fab34c8b3b8c1a510","tid":1696521,"uid":124690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T08:18:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/dmw9DPOwd6w\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fdmw9DPOwd6w&d=5WD1fpiCBK613UyTU9OnXxD7%2Fo0bOSfVmdYqJtNqH20%3D&h=edab7e0f\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/dmw9DPOwd6w</a><br />\n<br />\n【12:00】男生傷勢穩定<br />\n【00:20】新增動新聞<br />\n【22:12更新】領展回應《蘋果》查詢表示，事發於今午約4時10分，商場職員事發後已即時到場協助及慰問事主，並馬上召喚救傷車，及協助救護人員將事主送上救護車。保安錄像及在場途人報告顯示，個案或涉及有人不當使用扶手電梯。該公司呼籲訪客使用設施時，以安全為重。<br />\n<br />\n將軍澳厚德商場發生中學生從扶手電梯墮下重傷意外！據現場消息稱，一名中學生今午約4時，在商場地下扶手電梯旁玩耍，其間嘗試用雙手掹著一邊扶手梯吊上1樓，可惜疑失手從高位墮下受傷，一度躺在地上毫無反應。救護員接報到場，用擔架床將男生抬走送院。事後在場的同學亦協助警員調查。<br />\n<br />\n據目擊者Tony表示，當時與朋友在商場一樓快餐店吃包，聽到外面有人大叫，於是走出餐廳查看，則發現有一名穿校服的男生躺在樓下地面，相信他由扶手梯跌下，當時男生受傷不能動彈，其兩名女同學在旁不斷安慰。<br />\n<br />\n事後受傷男生的同學向《蘋果》提供一段事發時的片段，從片中可見，涉事男生當時雙手攀爬一邊扶手梯，儼如玩單槓姿勢，並隨扶手梯往上層一樓，當扶手梯差不多到達上層時，男童疑似「唔夠力」，一度起腳力撐，並欲伸手找住圍欄，可惜失手抓不到欄杆，整個人跌下。據受傷男生的同學表示，他在區內一間國際學校就讀中二，事發時與多名同學一起。<br />\n<br />\n記者晚上重返商場了解，發現受傷男生墮下的位置與地面的高度約有5米。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180105/large/1515157958_c058.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180105%2Flarge%2F1515157958_c058.jpg&h=351ff473&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一名中學生下午在厚德商場扶手梯玩耍，失手墮樓重傷。(讀者提供)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180105/large/1515160615_6590.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180105%2Flarge%2F1515160615_6590.jpg&h=4b6529f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n記者到商場了解，男生從扶手電梯近最高點，約5米高位置墮下。(姜偉康攝)<br />\n<br />\nLink: <a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180105/57671228?fbclid=IwAR1CKsf1GfNYjYPG92uIrS9wLLTToHYxW2c9Eri__Qh-GN2JxHT-0BuIOrg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180105%2F57671228%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR1CKsf1GfNYjYPG92uIrS9wLLTToHYxW2c9Eri__Qh-GN2JxHT-0BuIOrg&d=5WD1fpiCBK613UyTU9OnXxD7%2Fo0bOSfVmdYqJtNqH20%3D&h=a30dd4bf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180105%2F57671228%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR1CKsf1GfNYjYPG92uIrS9wLLTToHYxW2c9Eri__Qh-GN2JxHT-0BuIOrg&h=f3dfabd9\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180105/57671228?fbclid=IwAR1CKsf1GfNYjYPG92uIrS9wLLTToHYxW2c9Eri__Qh-GN2JxHT-0BuIOrg</a>"},{"pid":"088e39c76bde48811c7906caaa952eb0bd26c3f9","tid":1696521,"uid":124690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T08:19:50.000Z","msg":"腳落地再臀落"},{"pid":"fd5ba5126101ba2565c38f9a130667b13b0d4b95","tid":1696521,"uid":124690,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T08:20:45.000Z","msg":"點解要負皮"},{"pid":"ff826e66649d35acbcce1410b1f324997e63e243","tid":1696521,"uid":124690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T08:20:56.000Z","msg":"出嚟解釋下"},{"pid":"076df17d5cefcc416c2a5cb51ccdc9304052828c","tid":1696521,"uid":124690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T08:22:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af7afcaf09df87562f54feffa333f01315985e2e","tid":1696521,"uid":124690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T08:23:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.news.apple22222daily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180105/57671228?fbclid=IwAR1CKsf1GfNYjYPG92uIrS9wLLTToHYxW2c9Eri__Qh-GN2JxHT-0BuIOrg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.apple22222daily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180105%2F57671228%3Ffbclid%3DI